scene.message:
Ayase: Oh no!!{nl}
There's something huge{nl}
in here!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Ayase, heads up!{nl}
Leave this to us —{nl}
go hide!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: This is incredible...{nl}
Like something out{nl}
of sci-fi...{waitkey}{ret}

{nl}
Beyond here, if you find{nl}
anything suspicious, think{nl}
before you touch it!{waitkey}{clearbox}...Honestly, just thinking{nl}
about Inaba still makes{nl}
me furious!{waitkey}

Mark: Amazing...{nl}
To build something like this —{nl}
they mean
